    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Backrooms: The Lost Circus is a cooperative horror game for 1-4 players that carefully integrates elements of Backrooms, offering a unique take on this mysterious dimension rather than a direct mirror image of a familiar concept. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&gt;Fresh Perspective</strong> <br>This isn't your typical backrooms experience. It's a unique interpretation that sets it apart from the ordinary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&gt;One life</strong><br>And no indulgences!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&gt;Co-op</strong><br>Supports up to 4 players simultaneously. or solo only</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&gt;Stealth</strong><br>Sounds will attract something... better use it</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&gt;Proximity Voice Chat</strong><br>You can scream with your friends, but there is one thing...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&gt;Immersive AI</strong><br>AI's behavior is utterly unpredictable. Even I can't anticipate its next move.</p>",
